                     <td>
                        <h1>Campaign N'riahn's Misadventures</h1><br></td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                     <td><span class="body"><i>Speaking out of character, I am Umat Blackfeather, new member of the the EDC community.  After a long hiatus, my friends and
                              I have rediscovered Earthdawn and our gaming sessions have resumed.  I thought it would be great to record these experiences
                              here on EDC so other Earthdawn fans can share the laughs with us.  The following journal entries belong to N'riahn (pronounced
                              EN-ree-un), Human Elementalist and professional victim.</i></span></td>
                  </tr>
